headline: payabl. Joins Forces with London Lions to Support UK Basketball Growth
summary: LONDON, October 05, 2025--payabl., a leading European fintech offering payments and business accounts, has partnered with London’s premier basketball team – the London Lions – for the 2025–2026 season, marking a new commitment to supporting the growth of basketball in the UK and beyond.
